{"tid":2348943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"斥京脆弱獨裁 蓬佩奧促放人","createTime":"2021-01-01T07:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T07:47:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0a0307facdcebb767f3f7253df7f41913f2e9129","tid":2348943,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T07:02:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210101/SWGX72SNQZHJ5DXFU7ZGQAMY74/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210101%2FSWGX72SNQZHJ5DXFU7ZGQAMY74%2F&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=5f05c89d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210101%2FSWGX72SNQZHJ5DXFU7ZGQAMY74%2F&h=f08a8481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210101/SWGX72SNQZHJ5DXFU7ZGQAMY74/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n斥京脆弱獨裁 蓬佩奧促放人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5rfcMaGd1J7tavoVLbHiI2O1x0U=/1090x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SMWB4J2HEJFKJOGPCBTACMHCFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5rfcMaGd1J7tavoVLbHiI2O1x0U%3D%2F1090x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSMWB4J2HEJFKJOGPCBTACMHCFU.jpg&h=cc663cc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12港人送中案前日在深圳鹽田法院宣判，鄧棨然及喬映瑜分別判囚三年及兩年；李宇軒等八人則被判囚七個月。美國國務卿蓬佩奧（圖）昨要求中國立即放人。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：官派律師審訊後失聯 陷獄港青上訴無門  朱凱廸：司法程序欠妥 判刑皆屬不公<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台團體倡修例 加強援港人<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧昨發聲明，指美國強烈譴責深圳法院行動，並要求立即無條件釋放被判入獄的10人，又指事件表明北京向公民展示真面孔，「阻止本國人民離開的政權，無法以偉大或全球領袖自居。這僅僅是一種脆弱的獨裁政權，害怕自己人民」。案件再次暴露北京殘暴行為，公然無視其簽署的國際條約，並蔑視香港人民權利。<br />\n<br />\n另外，台灣公民團體昨在。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n經民連研究員江旻諺強調，台灣應針對性。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法新社／台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"b55493ea275f0a6fa95fcd7a5248d3c2e881395a","tid":2348943,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T07:05:48.000Z","msg":"蓬佩奧都就黎無得撈啦 講經咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3fc440e719fbbc3230bb30b3d9e81708974a073","tid":2348943,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b55493ea275f0a6fa95fcd7a5248d3c2e881395a","tid":2348943,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T07:05:48.000Z","msg":"蓬佩奧都就黎無得撈啦 講經咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T07:47:21.000Z","msg":"Let&rsquo;s see."}]}